chrome_driver = 'D:/bigdata/Jupyter_python/chromedriver.exe'
driver = webdriver.Chrome(chrome_driver)
driver.implicitly_wait(5) #   
# url = 'https://www.starbucks.co.kr/store/getStore.do?r=24F3U9PI7Q'
url = 'https://www.starbucks.co.kr/store/store_map.do'
# chrome driver    open
driver.get(url)

#   
starbucks = []

#   ' '  
search = driver.find_element_by_link_text(' ')
time.sleep(1)
search.click()

time.sleep(1)
#  class : set_sido_cd_btn  
search = driver.find_elements_by_class_name('set_sido_cd_btn')

for item in search:
    item.click()
    time.sleep(1)
    
    # data-sidocd='01~17' ~
    if '17' == item.get_attribute('data-sidocd'):
        #  
        src = driver.page_source
        
        # BeautifulSoup  
        soup = BeautifulSoup(src)
        name = soup.select('li[data-name]')
        for name_one in name:
            x = name_one['data-lat'] #  
            y = name_one['data-long'] #  
            z = name_one['data-name'] #  
            p = name_one.select_one('p').text.split('1522-3232')[0] #     crawling 
            starbucks.append({'name': z, 'address': p, 'lat': x, 'long':y}) # dict   
        time.sleep(1)
        
        #   
        driver.close()
    else:
        search2 = driver.find_element_by_link_text('')
        search2.click()
        driver.implicitly_wait(5)
        time.sleep(1)
        
        src = driver.page_source

        soup = BeautifulSoup(src)
        name = soup.select('li[data-name]')
        for name_one in name:
            x = name_one['data-lat']
            y = name_one['data-long']
            z = name_one['data-name']
            p = name_one.select_one('p').text.split('1522-3232')[0]
            starbucks.append({'name': z, 'address': p, 'lat': x, 'long':y})
        time.sleep(1)
        
        #      
        search3 = driver.find_element_by_link_text(' ')
        search3.click()
        time.sleep(1)

folium을 이용하여 지도에 표시¶

In [4]:
#  
map_list = folium.Map(location=[35.95, 128.25], zoom_start=7)

for item in starbucks:
    latitude = float(item['lat']) # 
    longtitude = float(item['long']) # 
    #   
    folium.Marker(
        location = [latitude, longtitude],
        popup = 'jijum : {}, addr : {}'.format(item['name'], item['address']),
        # icon       . 3 
        icon=folium.Icon(color='green', icon='glyphicon glyphicon-star')
    ).add_to(map_list)

데이터 엑셀 파일로 저장¶

In [5]:
# newline=''   
with open('starbucks.csv', 'w', newline='') as f:
    fieldnames =['', '', '', '']
    writer = csv.DictWriter(f, fieldnames=fieldnames)
    writer.writeheader()
    for i in starbucks:
        writer.writerow({'': i['name'], '': i['address'], '': i['lat'], '': i['long']})
